==制作==
[[File:Kelly_Asbury_and_Veronique_Culliford.jpg|thumb]]与[[沛优|沛优]]女儿的合影。]]
2012年5月10日，距《[[蓝精灵2|蓝精灵2]]》宣布制作两周，[[索尼動畫|索尼動畫]]和[[哥伦比亚影业|哥伦比亚影业]]已开发《蓝精灵3》的剧本，由{{le|凯利·柯克帕特里克|Karey Kirkpatrick}}和克里斯·波彻（{{lang|en|Chris Poche}}）<ref name=Variety>{{cite news|title=Sony already smurfing Smurfs 3|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118053808|accessdate=2015-01-17|work=Variety.com|date=2012-04-26|archive-date=2012-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121229013613/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118053808/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曾在前两作中饰演格格巫的[[汉克·阿扎里亚|汉克·阿扎里亚]]透露第三部“可能事实上处理所有角色闯入各自回头路的真正起源<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=106456 | title=Exclusive: The Smurfs 3 Will Include an Origin Story | publisher=ComingSoon.net | date=2013-07-14 | accessdate=2015-01-17 | last=Nemiroff | first=Perri | archive-date=2013-10-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012012129/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=106456 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。”有别于采用真人混合动画的前两部，第三部将完全采用动画，而且不是续集<ref name=PRNSonySlate/>。

2014年3月，[[凯利·艾西贝瑞|凯利·艾西贝瑞]]受聘为影片导演<ref name=PRNSonySlate/>。这部喜剧冒险片将呈现角色们的全新故事，探究蓝精灵的起源，场景设计更加贴近沛优的作品<ref name="PRNSonySlate">{{cite press release | url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/sony-pictures-animation-unveils-updated-production-slate-249842691.html | title=Sony Pictures Animation Unveils Updated Production Slate | publisher=PR Newswire | date=2014-03-12 | accessdate=2015-01-17 | author=Sony Pictures Animation | archive-date=2021-05-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506134800/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/sony-pictures-animation-unveils-updated-production-slate-249842691.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

影片由{{le|乔丹·克纳|Jordan Kerner}}和玛丽·艾伦·鲍德（{{lang|en|Mary Ellen Bauder}}）联合制片。2015年6月14日，索尼动画透露影片名《Get Smurfy》和首批剧照<ref name="DeadlineGetSmurfy" /><ref>{{cite news|title='Get Smurfy': First Look at Demi Lovato, Rainn Wilson-Voiced Film|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/get-smurfy-first-look-at-802378|accessdate=2015-09-05|work=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2015-06-14|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211183555/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/get-smurfy-first-look-at-802378|dead-url=no}}</ref>。片名后改为《蓝精灵：寻找神秘村》<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/02/11/smurfs-lost-village-sneak-peek-joe-manganiello-jack-mcbrayer/80182954/# | title=Sneak peek: Joe Manganiello, Jack McBrayer are new blue crew in 'Smurfs' | work=USA Today | date=2016-02-12 | accessdate=2016-02-14 | last=Alexander | first=Bryan | archive-date=2021-01-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122061649/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/02/11/smurfs-lost-village-sneak-peek-joe-manganiello-jack-mcbrayer/80182954/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年1月16日，[[曼迪·帕廷金|曼迪·帕廷金]]加盟剧组，配音饰演{{le|蓝爸爸|Papa Smurf}}<ref name="PatinkinCast">{{cite news | first1=Borys | last1=Kit | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/homeland-star-voice-papa-smurf-764395 | title='Homeland' Star to Voice Papa Smurf in Animated Movie | work=The Hollywood Reporter | date=2015-01-16 | accessdate=2015-01-17 | last2=Siegel | first2=Tatiana | archive-date=2021-01-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126125335/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/homeland-star-voice-papa-smurf-764395 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。6月14日，[[黛米·洛瓦托|黛米·洛瓦托]]和[[雷恩·威尔森|雷恩·威尔森]]加盟，分别饰演[[蓝妹妹|蓝妹妹]]和{{le|格格巫|Gargamel}}<ref name=DeadlineGetSmurfy>{{cite web|last1=Lowe|first1=Kinsey|title=‘Get Smurfy’ Unveiled: Demi Lovato Joins As Smurfette, Rainn Wilson As Gargamel|url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/get-smurfy-demi-lovato-as-smurfette-rainn-willson-as-gargamel-mandy-patinkin-as-papa-smurf-1201442625/|publisher=Deadline|accessdate=2015-09-05|date=2015-06-14|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226045126/https://deadline.com/2015/06/get-smurfy-demi-lovato-as-smurfette-rainn-willson-as-gargamel-mandy-patinkin-as-papa-smurf-1201442625/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年《[[蓝精灵2|蓝精灵2]]》上映后，两位此前分别为《蓝精灵》作品配音饰演蓝爸爸和笨笨的演员[[乔纳森·温特斯|乔纳森·温特斯]]和[[安东·叶利钦|安东·叶利钦]]不幸离世<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jonathan-winters-dies-at-87-438626 |title=Jonathan Winters Dies at 87 |publisher=Hollywood Reporter |first=Duane |last=Byrge |date=2013-04-12 |accessdate=2017-03-10 |archive-date=2021-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304160709/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jonathan-winters-dies-at-87-438626 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.theguardian.com/global/2016/jun/20/anton-yelchin-obituary-film-actor | work = The Guardian | accessdate = 2016-11-19 | title = Anton Yelchin obituary | archive-date = 2021-02-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210213125124/https://www.theguardian.com/global/2016/jun/20/anton-yelchin-obituary-film-actor | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2016年10月，{{le|克里斯托弗·莱纳兹|Christopher Lennertz}}宣布创作影片配乐<ref name="filmmusicreporter">{{cite web | url=http://filmmusicreporter.com/2016/10/11/christopher-lennertz-to-score-sony-pictures-animations-smurfs-the-lost-village/ | title=Christopher Lennertz to score Smurfs: The Lost Village | publisher=filmmusicreporter.com | accessdate=2016-10-11 | archive-date=2021-01-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129033135/http://filmmusicreporter.com/2016/10/11/christopher-lennertz-to-score-sony-pictures-animations-smurfs-the-lost-village/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>
。同年12月，据报道歌手[[梅根·崔娜|梅根·崔娜]]已录制影片插曲《I'm a Lady》，该曲以单曲形式发行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbizjunkies.com/music/meghan-trainor-song-smurfs-the-lost-village/|title=Meghan Trainor Writes "I'm a Lady" for 'Smurfs: The Lost Village'|date=2016-12-05|accessdate=2016-12-09|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031132705/https://www.showbizjunkies.com/music/meghan-trainor-song-smurfs-the-lost-village/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

